Cool PowerDNS Backend
=====================

This is a demonstration pipe backend for PowerDNS (http://powerdns.com), 
currently it can do these following task.

- Recurse to defined nameserver
- Manage domain request that usefull for filtering
- Implement record caching
- Connection to RDBMS
- Configurable with configuration file
- and some planned features...

To build this you will need these following libraries:

- hiredis, https://github.com/antirez/hiredis
- MySQL, http://mysql.org
- ldns, http://www.nlnetlabs.nl/projects/ldns/
- Glib, http://gtk.org

Ardhan
